</opentopic:map><concept break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " id="unique_1" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="zotero" oid="zotero" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">什么是Zotero</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc "/>
    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
        <p class="- topic/p ">
            Zotero由安德鲁·w·梅隆基金会，斯隆基金会以及美国博物馆和图书馆服务协会资助开发。它是一个开源的文献管理软件，帮助用户收集、管理、引用和共享研究资料。Zotero因其免费、开源和强大的功能而受到广泛欢迎，特别适合学术研究人员、学生和任何需要管理大量文献资料的用户。</p>
        <p class="- topic/p ">         Zotero的一些关键功能包括：跨平台支持（支持Windows、Mac OS
            X和Linux操作系统，作为Firefox、Chrome和Safari浏览器的插件）；集成浏览器插件（允许用户直接从浏览器中保存网页、PDF和其他在线资源。可以自动识别并抓取文献信息，如作者、标题、出版年等）；文献管理（用户可以创建文件夹和子文件夹来组织文献。支持添加标签和笔记，以便于分类和注释）；引用和格式化（支持数千种引用样式，如APA、MLA、Chicago等，还可以自动生成参考文献列表和文内引用）；
            同步和备份（通过Zotero的在线账户，用户可以在不同设备间同步文献库，支持手动或自动备份文献库）；共享和协作（可以创建公共或私有的文献库，与他人共享，支持团队协作，共同编辑和引用文献）；插件和扩展（支持与Microsoft
            Word、LibreOffice等文字处理软件集成，社区开发了多种插件和扩展，增强Zotero的功能）；开放API（提供API接口，允许开发者创建自定义工具和集成）；社区和支持（拥有活跃的社区，用户可以获取帮助和分享经验，官方论坛和文档提供详细的使用指南）；兼容性（可以导入和导出多种文献管理软件的文件格式，如EndNote、RIS等）。</p>
    </conbody>
</concept><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_2" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="windows_zotero" oid="windows_zotero" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">Windows如何下载安装Zotero</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Zotero最初是基于Firefox浏览器的插件，现在可以基于桌面独立安装，支持多种常见操作系统，如Linux，iOS，macOS和Windows等。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">本节主要介绍如何下载安装Windows 64位版本的Zotero。</context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">进入Zotero下载官网<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://www.zotero.org/" scope="external"><?ditaot usertext?>http://www.zotero.org/download/</xref>。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击页面左边"Zotero 7 Windows 版"模块蓝底白字"下载（64位）"按钮，如图所示<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/Windows下载1.jpg" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_iwt_m1h_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_iwt_m1h_mdc" placement="inline" width="170"/>。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">双击已经下载好的exe安装文件或是点击"打开文件"，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/windows下载2.jpg" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_g3k_3gh_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_g3k_3gh_mdc" placement="inline" width="200"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">等待安装文件解压，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/windows下载3.jpg" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_tbf_sgh_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_tbf_sgh_mdc" placement="inline" width="100"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">当弹出"你要允许此应用对你的设备进行更改吗"对话框时，请选择"是"。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">出现安装向导，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/windows下载4.jpg" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_lcp_bhh_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_lcp_bhh_mdc" placement="inline" width="120"/>，请点击"下一步"或"Next"。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">选择安装类型，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/windows下载5.jpg" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_wdz_nhh_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_wdz_nhh_mdc" placement="inline" width="150"/>，可按照个人需要选择Standard标准模式或Custom定制模式。默认安装目录为C盘中Program
                    Files（x86）下的Zotero，Standard模式无法修改安装目录；如选择Custom模式，点击"下一步"后软件将提示可以修改安装目录。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"Install"进行安装。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">安装完成后，点击<cmdname class="+ topic/keyword sw-d/cmdname ">Finish</cmdname>j即可打开Zotero。如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/windows下载6.jpg" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_l34_v3h_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_l34_v3h_mdc" placement="inline" width="150"/></cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_3" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="macos_zotero" oid="macos_zotero" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">macOS如何下载安装Zotero</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Zotero最初是基于Firefox浏览器的插件，现在可以基于桌面独立安装，支持多种常见操作系统，如Linux，iOS，macOS和Windows等。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">本节主要以Safari浏览器为例，介绍如何在macOS系统上下载安装Zotero。</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">进入Zotero官网<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://www.zotero.org/" scope="external"/>。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击页面中部红色背景"Download"按钮，如下图所示：</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/macOS下载1.png" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_k1w_jtg_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_k1w_jtg_mdc" placement="inline" width="100"/></info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在跳转的新页面中找到左方"Zotero 7 for Mac"模块，点击蓝底白字"Download"按钮，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/macOS下载2.jpg" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_m4h_ztg_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_m4h_ztg_mdc" placement="inline" width="157"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在弹出的"你要允许'www.zotero.org'上的下载吗"对话框中选择"允许"，然后等待下载。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">下载完成后，双击Zotero的dmg文件，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/macOS下载3.jpg" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_hvd_dwg_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_hvd_dwg_mdc" placement="inline" width="200"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在弹出框中将左侧的"Zotero"图标拖拽到右侧的"Drage Here to Install"里，然后等待Zotero拷贝到应用程序。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">双击应用程序中Zotero图标以打开软件，如图所示<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/macOS下载4.jpg" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_izm_rwg_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_izm_rwg_mdc" placement="inline" width="100"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">系统弹出对话框"'Zotero'是从互联网下载的App。您确定要打开它吗？"，请选择"打开"。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">当弹出"欢迎来到Zotero"页面时，表明已成功下载安装，此时官网会有如下提示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/apple/Desktop/Zotero下载安装及个性化设置/jpg/macOS下载5.jpg" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_nnq_gxg_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_nnq_gxg_mdc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task></map>